snippet.title: Best VGM 306 - Zone of the Enders 2 - Beyond the Bounds
snippet.description:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y81PyRX4ENA&fmt=18 for the HQ version!

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Zone of the Ender 2: The 2nd Runner
Beyond the Bounds (Intro)
